Enclosing class:
DefaultMemoryManageableSA<E>
public static class DefaultMemoryManageableSA.EveryQth<E>
extends Predicate<E>

This inner class provides a predicate for the remove filter for the load shedder. The method invoke returns true for every x-th method call on the average, where x is the ratio of p/q.

Method Detail

invoke

public boolean invoke(E argument)
Returns true or false according to the number of previous method calls. On the average the value true will be returned q/p times of the method calls, and accordingly the value false will be returned (1 - q/p) times of the method calls. The returned true-values are uniformly distributed among the several method calls.

Overrides:
invoke in class Predicate<E>
Parameters:
argument - This argument is irrelevant, it may be null.
Returns:
the result of the predicate as a primitive boolean value.
